        "###1. Matriz de adyacencia ponderada $洧녥_{ij}$\n",
        "$$I1\\hspace{1,5cm}I2\\hspace{0,4cm}I3\\hspace{0,8cm}I4\\hspace{0,8cm}I5$$\n",
        "$$W_{ij}=\\begin{bmatrix}\n",
        "0 &0.8  &0  &0.6  &0.7  \\\\\n",
